{"comments":"ContextMenu — Right-click property inspector for any element.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nAt billion-agent scale, the context menu is the **interface between\nagents and reality**. When an agent right-clicks an element, they see:\n\n1. **Applicable property groups** — Only what's relevant to this element\n2. **Bounded editors** — Sliders, toggles, pickers with explicit limits\n3. **Composable effects** — Add glow, shadow, motion paths\n4. **No infinite loops** — Motion always has start and end keyframes\n\n## Integration\n\nUses Schema atoms:\n- `Gestural.ContextMenu` for menu state and positioning\n- `Element.Context` for property applicability\n- `PropertySection` for collapsible groups\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Element.Compound.ContextMenu as ContextMenu\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Element.Context as Context\n\n-- Create context menu for a swatch\nContextMenu.contextMenu\n  [ ContextMenu.context Context.swatchContext\n  , ContextMenu.position (Gestural.AtPointer 100.0 200.0)\n  , ContextMenu.isOpen state.menuOpen\n  , ContextMenu.onClose CloseMenu\n  , ContextMenu.onPropertyChange HandlePropertyChange\n  ]\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render a context menu for an element.\n\nThe menu shows property groups applicable to the element type,\nwith editors for each property in the group.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","ContextMenu"],"ContextMenuProp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag